        <updateDate>2019-08-29T21:29:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Opioid Emergency Response Act</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes a series of programs and requirements relating to opioid use, including programs to incentivize the use of opioid alternatives; the bill also creates a new, sixth schedule of controlled substances that includes specified synthetic fentanyl-related substances.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
